title: ALL UTILIES AND INTERNET INCLUDED BEAUTIFUL SINGLE FAMILY HOME
posting_body: ['Gorgeous 3 Bedroom/2 Bath house, built in 2010', 'Located in a beautiful equestrian gated (with 24/7 guard) community with wooded preserves and lake access', '2.5 miles from International Polo Club', '5 miles from Wellington Green Mall and Wellington Regional Medical Center', "Minutes from Whole Foods, Trader Joe's, Publix, Target, many restaurants, and shopping.", 'Located in A-rated Wellington school district', 'Includes:', '- Large 1 car garage', '- Marble floors throughout', '- Granite counters, stainless steel appliances', '- Vaulted ceilings', '- Washer/dryer', '500Sf  covered screen patio', 'Rent: $4000/month', 'rent includes all utilities (electricity, water, sewer, trash), internet, and lawn maintenance', 'Requires first, last month rent + one month security deposit', 'Pets welcome!', '(Pet fee applies)', 'Please contact for further info.']
